\newlabel{tab:cost}{{5}{8}{Wallclock cost (single H100, $T=7$ tasks, 7-task evaluation): merge construction + full evaluation on the 7-task benchmark. Times exclude CLIP-text-embedding pre-computation. Methods that require per-task calibration data also incur an additional forward pass over a calibration set}{table.caption.10}{}}
